{"tid":1787261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【撐警惹禍】藝人撐警被割席 葵涌茶記曹永廉有份？員工答得含糊：只知大老闆有錢過佢","createTime":"2019-12-17T21:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T00:55:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"62050f7c919ec94df7a8bd5ad30a2b59f1d1d1ad","tid":1787261,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:37:02.000Z","msg":"上星期，一班藝人到警察總部支持警察，原本行程低調，怎料有豬隊友發帖，把當日拍的相片公開，更立即被同行的人用粗口大鬧，成為熱話。事件被各大媒體公開後，同行的姚瑩瑩、曹永廉被各大品牌立即割席，網民亦立刻起底，把藝人有份經營的餐廳公開，其中包括楊明的湯品專門店「燉」，照片站在最前，早前大鬧反政府人士的曹永廉當然有份。<br />\n<br />\n早於2013年，就有報導指曹永廉和家人在順利警察宿舍商場開設茶餐廳，名「茶記冰室」，雖然該店早已結業，但據傳他是葵涌一間同名茶餐廳「茶記冰室」的老闆之一。記者到店舖時查問曹永廉是否老闆，店員表示自己不清楚。記者在晚上再致電，店員雖沒有直接否認，不斷回覆「無」，當記者問到「無」是否等於「不是」，店員答案顯得反覆混沌：「現在就算回覆你，我也是答不知道。沒有這一回事，據我們所知是沒有。你問他本人，我們只是打工，我只知我們大老闆比他更有錢。」<br />\n<br />\n茶記冰室<br />\n地址：葵涌石蔭路60號金石樓地下2號舖<br />\n電話：2253 4168<br />\n營業時間：7am-10pm<br />\n詳情： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PSAz3x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PSAz3x&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Buj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=10e3df0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PSAz3x</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191217/large/1576579967_fb68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576579967_fb68.jpg&h=ee1f8fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20191217/6CCUV2D2XTSWXPZGKQVU2OTUE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20191217%2F6CCUV2D2XTSWXPZGKQVU2OTUE4%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Buj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2780283c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20191217%2F6CCUV2D2XTSWXPZGKQVU2OTUE4%2F&h=8bfc1bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20191217/6CCUV2D2XTSWXPZGKQVU2OTUE4/</a>"},{"pid":"8d13b32b8d05aa11a6a368a67968e293ac6f2c2f","tid":1787261,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:12:55.000Z","msg":"當左藍先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1be9a101c3d2bd64c1c9117c6fc7e7cda6fe44","tid":1787261,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d13b32b8d05aa11a6a368a67968e293ac6f2c2f","tid":1787261,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:12:55.000Z","msg":"當左藍先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:19:07.000Z","msg":"正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d408b163219701fcfe045673e41db2cc269d25cf","tid":1787261,"uid":54264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:22:50.000Z","msg":"支持警察好失禮咩 做咩唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef06732a168b4f772f9b1c664ad23cdfab7fa31","tid":1787261,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:24:56.000Z","msg":"咁曖昧咪當你係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a4214f99171a6f3012526cf3927fa95676b79a","tid":1787261,"uid":1891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T22:25:21.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n毋忘元朗恐襲事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RRKyxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RRKyxN.jpg&h=fcfe2918&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSrB86f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSrB86f.jpg&h=51458dba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ceb88ac7655bcc12841e038695eba164192c96d","tid":1787261,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T23:04:24.000Z","msg":"唔係就唔係，支吾以對<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默🈲❌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784354</a>"},{"pid":"3241c2df79b5dd0668972d87a48c1